articles.title: Stocks pull lower at end of record year for markets
articles.content: Still, all three indices logged solid gains for the full year. "Generally speaking, 2025 was a spectacular year for equities," said Briefing.com analyst Patrick O'Hare. London's benchmark FTSE 100 index jumped more than 21 percent...
